<div class="text-center">
    <img class="logo" src="~/logo2.jpg" alt="Retro style word art that says 'Battle of Champions'" />
       <h2 class="retro-animated">Welcome to the Battle of Champions data storage application!</h2>
    
      <p class="retro-static">  If this is your first time using the app, please click <span class="emphasis">Champions</span> or <span class="emphasis">Equipment</span> in the Nav Bar, then click the
