    </p>
    <p class="retro-static"> After that, go ahead and add some pieces of <span class="emphasis">Equipment</span> to the database first.</p>
    <p class="retro-static"> Then add some <span class="emphasis">Champions</span> after you have created some equipment to give them.</p>
    <img class="image" src="~/hero.jpg" alt="Retro style pixel art of several fighter characters" />
</div>
